#

Braised Pork Shoulder with Garlic Mashed Potatoes and Rich Red Wine Gravy

$25.99
820 kcal
Difficulty: 70%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

Comfort FoodSlow-CookedHearty

Description

Tender braised pork shoulder served over creamy garlic mashed potatoes, drizzled with a luscious red wine gravy.

Ingredients

  • Pork shoulder: 3 lbs
  • Garlic cloves: 6, minced
  • Yellow potatoes: 2 lbs
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Unsalted butter: 1/2 cup
  • Red wine: 2 cups
  • Beef stock: 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Fresh thyme: 2 sprigs
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
